[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m     <div id="adicional">[m
[32m+[m[32m     <p>Donec purus ipsum, posuere id, venenatis at, <span>placerat ac,[m
[32m+[m[32m     lorem</span>. Curabitur blandit, eros sed gravida aliquet, risus justo[m
